comments: LeVert (BKN) establishes himself in the front court within eight seconds of the possession's origin.
Simons (POR) and Dinwiddie (BKN) engage and disengage off ball without affecting the other's FOM.
Dinwiddie (BKN) rests his hand against Lillard's (POR) backside and makes marginal contact as the pick is set.
Lillard (POR) makes marginal contact with Irving's (BKN) upper half that does not affect Irving's ability to defend.

After the made free throw, Dinwiddie (BKN) establishes himself in Simons' (POR) path and slightly extends his right arm into Simons' front, but contact is marginal. Simons and Allen (BKN) then make incidental foot-to-foot contact.
Irving (BKN) moves laterally into Lillard's (POR) path and initiates contact to his side after his gather.
Simons (POR) makes marginal contact to Irving's (BKN) front that does not affect his SQBR.
Simons (POR) maintains legal guarding position during Irving's (BKN) drive toward the basket.
Lillard (POR) makes marginal contact with his left hand to LeVert's (BKN) front and does not alter his body trajectory as he returns to the floor following the release of the jump shot attempt.
Allen (BKN) makes contact with Lillard's (POR) front/right arm after he gathers the ball in his left hand, affecting his driving shot attempt.
Simons (POR) makes marginal contact with Irving's (BKN) backside as they move past the perimeter and as the defensive switch occurs.
Allen (BKN) firms up on his right leg within the frame of his body and does not deliver the contact, some of which may occur to Simons' leg.
Simons (POR) maintains a legal guarding position and makes marginal contact with Harris (BKN) that does not affect his drive to the lane and shot attempt.
LeVert (BKN) moves alongside McCollum's (POR) path and maintains legal guarding position as McCollum loses control of the ball on his own.
Simons (POR) briefly has his hands around Irving's (BKN) midsection, but slides them off without affecting Irving's FOM.
LeVert (BKN) moves forward into Lillard's (POR) side and initiates contact during his upward shooting motion.
Simons (POR) makes marginal contact with Irving (BKN) that does not affect his drive to the lane and shot attempt.
Irving (BKN) makes marginal contact with his left foot to Simons' (POR) front that does not affect his ability to defend.
Irving (BKN) makes marginal body contact with Lillard (POR) that does not affect his SQBR.
Irving (BKN) makes contact with Lillard's (POR) left leg during his upward shooting motion.
As Irving (BKN) breaks for the inbound pass, he and Lillard (POR) come together on the perimeter and make incidental body contact.
Bazemore (POR) briefly engages with Dinwiddie (BKN) during the inbound.
Irving (BKN) and Simons (POR) engage and disengage without affecting the other's FOM during the inbound.
Dinwiddie (BKN) firms up in his screening position in Simons' (POR) path and does not deliver the contact.
Hezonja (POR) commits the take foul on Harris (BKN).
